reviews.review_text: Recording Info Neumann KM 140 -> Aerco pre-amp -> Sony D-10.. FOB.. capsules in mesh baseball hat.. 110° ortf.. recorded by Dominic Tringale and Roger Jones for sure. I can't remember if Keith Litzenberger and/or Jim Cowen was with us
